        "pitch_and_presentation": 5
    },

    "final_verdict": "Historical Voices presents an interesting concept with moderate potential for educational impact. The project scores above average on creativity due to its life-stages feature but falls short on technical implementation and presentation. To improve, the team should:\n1. Complete the ElevenLabs API integration\n2. Develop unique technical features beyond API integration\n3. Add demonstrations and metrics to their presentation\n4. Focus on historical accuracy and data validation\n5. Establish clear differentiation from existing solutions\nThe current implementation is promising but needs significant refinement to reach its full potential."
